# == About me

# I am an associate professor at the [http://gts.uc3m.es Signal Processing Group (GTS)] in Universidad Carlos III de Madrid (UC3M), Spain. I received the Ph.D. degree in Telecommunications from [http://us.es University of Sevilla] in 2011 and I joined UC3M at 2012. I have been a visiting researcher at [http://www.epfl.ch École Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne] (Switzerland), [http://www.nd.edu Notre Dame University] (USA) and [http://www.ensea.fr École Nationale Supérieure de l'Electronique et de ses Applications]  (France). 

== Research interests
-  Probabilistic Machine Learning  and efficient inference methods
-  Deep probabilistic models
-  Applications in personalized medicine and life-sciences


