{Machine Learning Summer School (MLSS) (August 2025)}

I had the pleasure of being one of the organizers of [https://eventosdiee.ucsp.edu.pe/mlss/ MLSS 2025 in Arequipa, Perú]. An outstanding group of speakers and students came together for 13 days of engaging seminars and discussions. It was truly a wonderful experience.
